<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Acrobatic_gymnastic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A sport that combines acrobatics and choreography performed individually and collectively, to music. Pyramids are the special feature of this discipline. It requires strength, flexibility, agility and acrobatic skills. The exercises are performed on a platform similar to that used in artistic gymnastics." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Acrobatic_gymnastic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
