<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_classes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline combining fitness and acrobatics. It allows you to demonstrate your ability to perform a series of dynamic movements to music. A truly creative discipline, it requires you to capture the audience's attention and harmoniously combine dance elements with elements of difficulty. Movements can be performed individually, in duets, trios or groups (5 gymnasts)." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_classes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_classes> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Aerobic classes" .
