<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_exercise> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline practiced by repeating sequences of light-to-moderate intensity activities over extended periods of time." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_exercise> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
