<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Aerobic_gymnastic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline combining fitness and acrobatics. It requires strength, endurance, and flexibility. Gymnasts perform to music lasting 1 minute 30 seconds on a surface of 7 x 7 meters for individuals, and 10 x 10 meters for groups. The movements can be performed individually, in pairs, in trios, or in groups (5 gymnasts)." .
