<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Artistics_gymnastics> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline for women practiced on 4 apparatus: the vault, the uneven bars, the balance beam, and the floor. The combination of these 4 apparatuses makes it a very complete discipline. For men, it is practiced on 6 apparatus: the floor, the pommel horse, the rings, the vault, the parallel bars, and the high bar." .
