<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Crossfit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Trademark for cross-training promoted by the company CrossFit Inc. In everyday language, the term CrossFit is associated with a multidisciplinary sport practice. CrossFit is built around ten athletic skills: cardiovascular and respiratory endurance, muscular endurance, strength, flexibility, power, speed, agility, coordination, balance, and accuracy.\"" .
