<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_Korea_traditional> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Dance performance describe magnificently costumed male and female shamans who sing and dance to musical accompaniment, drawing the heavenly spirits down to earth through their performance" .
