<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_ballet> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A type of dancing where carefully organized movements tell a story or express an idea, or a theatre work that uses this type of dancing: Dancers often wear elaborate costumes and pointe shoes, which allow them to dance on the tips of their toes" .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_ballet> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
