<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_flamenco> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance> .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_flamenco> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A multifaceted dance that blends various cultural influences, including Islamic, Andalusian, Gypsy, Sephardic, and Arab traditions. It combines elements of singing, guitar playing, dancing, and hand clapping" .
