<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Dance_hip_hop> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Street dance, combining elements of modern dance, tap dance, and swing. It is most often performed to hip-hop music and includes a wide range of freestyle movements, with three main styles: breakdancing, popping, and locking." .
