<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Gymnastics_tumbling> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline in which gymnasts perform a series of acrobatics on a dynamic track. The Tumbling track is 25 meters long and 2 meters wide. Gymnasts must perform a sequence of 8 consecutive acrobatic moves, ending with a \"dismount.\" The landing area measures 6 meters by 4 meters." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Gymnastics_tumbling> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
