<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Roller-skate_figure_skating> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A sport discipline performed with quad roller skates on a smooth and flat surface measuring at least 20 x 40 meters (parquet, smooth concrete, terrazzo, etc.). It can be practiced individually or in pairs. This is a technical and acrobatic discipline that requires speed, power, precision, and artistic expression. Athletes can compete in compulsory figures or free skating.\nEach event is judged separately. An athlete participating in both events will also receive a combined ranking." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Roller-skate_figure_skating> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
