<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Rowing_heavyweight> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Disciplines of rowing. Technically, there is no heavyweight division, in the same sense that boxing or wrestling have heavyweight categories. Anything lower than 160 pounds for men and 130 pounds for women are classed as lightweight. Anything above those limits will be considered NOT lightweight and are categorized as open weight class.\n" .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Rowing_heavyweight> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
