<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Running_long_distance> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A discipline that refers to running over a distance of at least 5 kilometers. Physiologically, it is an effort primarily involving aerobic metabolic processes and requiring physical endurance capabilities." .
