<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Running_middle_distance> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Track races longer than sprints, ranging from 500 meters up to two miles (3,218,688 meters). The standard middle distances are the 800 meters, 1500 meters and mile run, although the 3000 meters may also be classified as a middle-distance event." .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Running_middle_distance> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
