<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Rythmic_gymnastics> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Sport practised to music using apparatus: hoop, ball, clubs, ribbon and rope. In competition, it can be practised either individually or in a group of 5 gymnasts. It is a complete discipline combining flexibility, grace and skill." .
