<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Taekwondo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "A martial art of South Korean origin that differs from other arts in that it is highly specialised in kicking techniques. To avoid serious injury, martial artists wear a wide range of protective gear when fighting. It is the only Olympic combat sport that allows kicking. " .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Taekwondo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-category-vocab/Sport> .
<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Taekwondo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Taekwondo" .
