<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/sport-vocab/Urban_dance> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#description> "Street dance combining sport and art. It takes the form of battles between individuals or teams. The dancers take it in turns to perform a series of leg movements and figures on the floor" .
